WHAT PROBLEM IT SOLVES
Resolves the confusion caused by the Nikon‑RED codec partnership. Provides
a single, auditable body file that handles both the native N‑Log and the
RED‑LUT‑transformed paths. Ensures that Z9 footage linearized via GIOP
matches the original scene light to within 10⁻⁶ relative error regardless
